title: Dell Inspiron 17 5721 Windows 8 x64 Recovery Disks
description:
This is the full recovery disk set for Dell 17 5721. These disks will fully restore all software originally installed on this model. This is Windows 8 x64. This will recreate all factory partitions as they were, including the recovery partition.

These are the recovery disks created when you first get the computer and contain no updates. 

There are different variations of these recovery disks and this may not contain all drivers or software shipped with your particular model. Your laptop should have came from the factory with Windows 8 for this to activate properly. This may only work on a 1 TB or larger hard drive.

This may also work on similar models.

Disk 1 MD5; 85C8FAC9DE4BC3835F036ADCB8BDA6F0

Disk 2 MD5; FC02E82E9505EC2F61B73A25AC4CDDA9

Disk 3 MD5; 14B59F8FC3FC2E8CCD00D018F683F780

PLEASE SEED UNTIL AT LEAST 1:1 RATIO TO KEEP THIS TORRENT ALIVE FOR A LONG TIME TO COME.
